author: Kathy Gannon / AP
title: China Sends Medical Personnel, Supplies to Pakistan to Combat Coronavirus
description: China sent a plane with medical personnel and supplies Saturday to help Pakistan combat the outbreak of the coronavirus.
content:
(ISLAMABAD) — China sent a plane loaded with medical personnel and supplies Saturday to help Pakistan fight the spread of the coronavirus in one of the world’s most populous nations.
